                   String msg,

        CRN140317 - Adding this method so that all data transmission back to the user is wrapped in a try/catch. The goal of this is to assure that if the user closes their browser window, this jsp can continue working and complete the broadcast transmissions.
        Parameters:
        out - JspWriter to use to output the message
        msg - message to output
